data.description: Perfect first time home 3 bedroom and office, 2 full bath as well as fenced in yard with plenty of parking space.  First floor laundry hook up. Many upgrades including brand new gutters, new windows, wood floor restoration, new sink, toilet, tile work, custom shelving throughout. Whole house spot insulated, warm and cozy in the winter.
